$Id$

What is this?
-------------
An experiment on how far I can go using JavaScript in an object-
oriented way.

Goal
----
Create a JavaScript "base library" based on the principles of
the XP framework (object-oriented, documented, easy, useful but
generic classes).

Resources
---------
- http://www.u.arizona.edu/~jscully/javafication.html
  "Well, Here it is ... Javafied Javascript ..."

- http://www.crockford.com/#javascript
  "JavaScript: The Wrrrld's Most Misunderstood Programming Language"
  "Classical Inheritance in JavaScript"
  "Remedial JavaScript"

